item.title: Exterior Hand Wash
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: We hand wash your paint with a pH neutral shampoo, we remove dirt without damaging paint or trims. Your car’s exterior is chamois-dried to prevent water marks forming on the paint and high pressure air is used to remove water from panel joins and trim.

item.title: Interior Vacuum
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: We vacuum your seats, including all the creases in your fabric or leather, carpets and mats. We will not miss under your seats.

item.title: Windows In & Out
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: We clean the inside of your windscreen and other interior windows. We give special attention to the rear view mirror and any vanity mirrors. If you have got a glass sunroof that will be cleaned too.

item.title: Paint Protection
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Paint Protection helps preserve a car’s original manufacturers paint. Using our high quality paint protectant can give your exterior the added strength, preserving it that glow and shine over many years to come.

item.title: Rain-X Complete
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Rain-X Complete is a surface protectant designed to add premium shine, protection and water repellency to glass, paint, trim and chrome. After 24 hours Rain-X Complete actually cures onto the surfaces of your vehicle for better adhesion and enhanced protection.
